data.description: Tucked away in the picturesque enclave of Bigfork, Montana, this expansive 5-acre property offers unmatched privacy at the end of a secluded road. Designed for those with a passion for nature, it's a haven for wildlife and domestic animals alike, beckoning you to breathe life into its potential. With minimal covenants, this home comes equipped with a myriad of outbuildings tailored for diverse animal accommodations. The centerpiece: a two-story residence offering 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 baths. The master suite invites relaxation with its airy vaulted ceilings and a luxurious jetted tub in the en-suite bathroom. While you'll feel worlds away from the hustle and bustle, conveniences are mere minutes away. Dive into this unique blend of rural charm and modern living. For more information or to schedule a showing call Kevin Croteau at 406-270-6737 or your Real Estate professional. Information provided is from sources deemed to be reliable & accurate but not warranted by listing agent/office.  It is subject to change without notice.  All prospective purchasers & agents should check for accuracy of all statements contained herein to their own satisfaction.
